OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry in the
OL,6,Fnorth, with clear periods leading to
OL,7,Fsome fog or freezing fog in places and
OL,8,Ffrost. Areas of low cloud are more
OL,9,Flikely in the south, with this thick
OL,10,Fenough for a little drizzle at times.
OL,11,FLight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FBrightest in the north first
OL,14,Fthing, however extensive low cloud
OL,15,Fshould spread from the south to bring
OL,16,Fa little rain. A milder day than on
OL,17,FSaturday for most. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
