OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fmurky Monday. Breezier through
OL,7,FTuesday, with cloud breaks developing
OL,8,Fahead of late rain. Wet and windy into
OL,9,FWednesday, but soon brighter and
OL,10,Fblustery. Temperatures above average
OL,11,Fday and night.
